name: Tez Dizpenser ⁄ Neptune ⁄ SYSTEMA SOLARIS ⁄ #2
description: Meet Neptune. SYSTEMA SOLARIS is a series of 10 works that captures the sheer beauty and size of our solar system. Each unique 1 of 1 Tez Dizpenser showcases that celestial body's scale, moon(s), rings, color and its distant view of the sun. Join me on this space-bound voyage. Collect them all! 〔 Diameter: 30,775 mi 〕〔 Length of Day: 16.1 hr 〕〔 Distance from Sun: 2.8 billion mi 〕〔 Average Temperature: -330°F 〕〔 Number of Moons: 14 〕 Twitter: @cmilburndesign – Clubhouse: @codestrong
